	<p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0373b09"/><lb ed="T" n="0373b09"/><persName key="A002245">釋慧亮</persName>，姓<ptr target="fn08"/>姜，先名<persName key="A002245">顯亮</persName>，為<placeName key="PL000000022347">東阿</placeName><persName key="A002229">靖公</persName>弟子。<lb ed="T" n="0373b10"/>少有清譽，時人呼<persName key="A002229">靖</persName>為<persName key="A002229">大師</persName>，<persName key="A002245">亮</persName>為<persName key="A002245">小師</persName>。雖<lb ed="T" n="0373b11"/>年望未逮，而風軌繼之。後立寺於<placeName key="PL000000020627">臨淄</placeName>，講<lb ed="T" n="0373b12"/>《法華》、大小《品》、《十地》等。學徒雲聚、千里命駕。後<lb ed="T" n="0373b13"/>過江止<placeName key="PL000000008703">何園寺</placeName>、<persName key="A002645">顏<ptr target="fn09"/>延</persName>、<persName key="A002990">張緒</persName>眷德留連，每歎<lb ed="T" n="0373b14"/>曰：「<persName key="A001503">安</persName>、<persName key="A002193">汰</persName>吐珠玉於前，<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>、<persName key="A002245">亮</persName>振金聲於後，清<lb ed="T" n="0373b15"/>言妙緒，將絕復興。」<date key="j18912671893480" notAfter-iso="0472" notBefore-iso="0466">太始</date>之初，<placeName key="PL000000008702">莊嚴<ptr target="fn10"/>寺</placeName>大集，<lb ed="T" n="0373b16"/>簡閱義士上首千人，勅<persName key="A002245">亮</persName>與<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>遞為法主，<lb ed="T" n="0373b17"/>當時宗匠無與競焉。</p><p><date key="j18938651895488" notAfter-iso="0477" notBefore-iso="0473">宋元徽中</date>卒，春秋六十<lb ed="T" n="0373b18"/>三矣。著〈玄通論〉，今行於世。</p>
